## Limitations
The findings are based on available data and reports, which may not capture the full scope of the issue across different regions. Additionally, the rapidly evolving nature of the pandemic means that the situation in hospitals can change quickly, potentially affecting the relevance of the data over time. Further research and updated data would be necessary for a more comprehensive understanding of the ongoing challenges faced by healthcare systems globally.

